import React from 'react';

import {
  Container,
  Title,
  Form,
  Input,
  SubmitButton,
  TodoList,
  TodoListItem,
  Checkbox,
  TodoDescription,
} from './styles';

const App: React.FC = () => (
  <Container>
    <Title>Tarefas</Title>

    <Form>
      <Input placeholder="Insira uma nova tarefa.." />
      <SubmitButton type="submit">Salvar</SubmitButton>
    </Form>

    <TodoList>
      <TodoListItem>
        <Checkbox type="checkbox" />
        <TodoDescription>Ir ao shopping</TodoDescription>
      </TodoListItem>
      <TodoListItem>
        <Checkbox type="checkbox" />
        <TodoDescription>Ir ao shopping</TodoDescription>
      </TodoListItem>
      <TodoListItem>
        <Checkbox type="checkbox" />
        <TodoDescription>Ir ao shopping</TodoDescription>
      </TodoListItem>
    </TodoList>
  </Container>
);

export default App;
